[Better to be safe than sorry. The test-positive material from the Navy
site has been sent to USAMRIID and CDC for confirmation. One can speculate
endlessly on this to little purpose until the laboratory work is complete.
Logically they will be checking for plasmid content just in case the cause
was Sterne vaccine spores. If it is a true repeat of 2001 that will raise a
number of questions, good, bad and embarrassing. If it was a false
positive, we learn the need for better surveillance. - Mod.MHJ]
